      "review_summary": "The PR adds plugin metadata snapshot memoization fixes and threads manifest registry, discovery, and install records through provider/runtime/auto-enable paths to reduce TUI cold-start plugin-system work.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the review finding: current main already has a focused same-process derived-manifest edit test, and source inspection of PR head shows the memo no longer stores the derived watched-file state that made that test pass. I did not run tests because this review is read-only.",
